description:
Risen 2: Dark Waters REPACK-SashHD


General Information:

Released : 2012 
Genre : RPG / 3D / 3rd Person 
Developer : Piranha Bytes 
Publisher : Deep Silver  Akella
Language: English/Russian
Repack: SashHD
Source: SKIDROW


Description: 

The game is Risen 2: Dark Waters, devoted to pirate adventures on the numerous islands, combines popular classic RPG-mechanics of the original game, Risen with 
a fresh theme. RPG from the third person in the dark and gloomy universe Risen 2: Dark Waters maintains the characteristics of first and Risen offers many options for each task, so each player can choose the path to your liking. 


System Requirements:

OS: Windows XP (Service pack 3), Windows Vista (Service pack 1) and Windows 7 
Processor: Dual Core with 3 GHz 
Memory: 4 GB System RAM 
Video Card: 1024 MB Radeon 4890 / GeForce GTX 260 
HDD: 7 GB


Repack Features:

* At the heart of - [Rus / Eng] Rip-Steam version of the game * - 1.0
* Installation time - 7.6 
* Close all the applications when installing.
* Small Size 
* Installation guide dedicated.


